cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with machine learning models and their vulnerability to attacks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The specific task of stealing functionality of black box models is related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of reinforcement learning also suggests a possible connection to social and information networks (cs.SI).
